      <h1>REAL environment</h1>
      <p>This is the experimental Web-enabled course-support environment,
		  initiated at the Faculty of Science and Technology (FST).
		  This system, targeted for undergraduate students, carries the connotation
		  of a rich environment for active learning, and hence its name REAL.<br> The REAL environment
		  is designed to encourage student responsibility, to make learning meaningful,
		  to support knowledge construction, and to allow learner assessment,in the specific
		   curriculums of their study. </p>
